# K530 – Build and test

This keyboard lives under **qmk_firmware/keyboards/redragon/k530**. After changing keymaps, config, or rules, verify the build.

## Test the build

From the **qmk_firmware** root (parent of `keyboards/`), run:

```bash
qmk compile -kb redragon/k530 -km default
qmk compile -kb redragon/k530 -km via
```

Run both so default and VIA keymaps compile. Fix any compile errors before considering the change done.
